## Starting Layla

```powershell
cd agent
uvicorn main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000
```

Or double-click `START.bat` (Windows) / run `bash start.sh` (Linux/macOS).

Web UI: `http://localhost:8000/ui`  
TUI: `cd agent && python tui.py`  
CLI: `python layla.py wakeup`
